Alright, I think the floor issue is due to lines 980-981 in `EditorView.cc`, function `OnAddLevel`.

```c++
    // Select -> deselect to trigger change
    wallSegmentItem->setSelected(true);
    wallSegmentItem->setSelected(false);
```

I changed these lines to `wallSegmentItem->Set3dTransparency(0.4);` and it appeared to fix the problem. The changes are in branch [buildingedit_change_level_transparency_louise_jackie](#!/osrf/gazebo/branch/buildingedit_change_level_transparency_louise_jackie).
